{"tid":1973430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】河南郟縣「二度封城」 3醫生被驗出是「隱形病人」致53人隔離","createTime":"2020-04-15T07:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:48:45.000Z","uid":219010,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eff86dd0ad9ff75252cd8381ba53430727e65e64","tid":1973430,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】河南郟縣「<span style=\"color: red;\">二度封城</span>」 3醫生被驗出是「隱形病人」致53人隔離<br />\n<br />\n河南省郟縣人民醫院3名醫生被檢測為「無症狀感染者」，郟縣防疫辦公室昨天（1日）宣佈全縣再度封村、封小區（社區），所有人員憑證出入，除超市、醫院、市場外的商店一律停業。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【武漢肺炎】衝出國際？ 港女稱獲新加坡友人贈CSi口罩<br />\n<br />\n郟縣此舉被認為是「二度封城」，昨晚引起關注。據《南華早報》報道，猶如宵禁等級的封鎖，已於3月31日起實施。而同在3月31日，河南省官方已要求加強無症感染者管理。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，郟縣交通運輸局一名官員確認了全縣進入封閉狀態。他說，「這時候最好不要進出郟縣，沒有人能夠進出」。<br />\n<br />\n當地一名23歲的王小姐表示，她是在前天（31日）下午被村裡通知這項封鎖令。官方要求民眾購買日用品及蔬菜，為封城作準備。而她很擔心疫情的新發展，因為郟縣人民醫院離自己家只有約2公里。<br />\n<br />\n根據內地媒體報道，事件起因是一名河南省漯河市的王姓女清潔人員，曾於3月21日搭乘長途客運前往郟縣，由一名郟縣人民醫院的張姓醫生駕車搭載前往掃墓，兩人並一同用餐3次。事後，王女在28日確診為武漢肺炎病例。<br />\n<br />\n再經追查發現，張姓醫生早在3月13日晚間，與同院的劉姓、周姓醫生在飯店同桌用餐。其中，劉姓醫生曾有武漢旅遊史，回郟縣後即自行隔離14天，用餐時已隔離期滿。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，郟縣人民醫院25日對參與防疫的一線醫護人員進行體檢，在核酸篩查中發現張、周二名醫生是「無症狀感染者」。至於劉姓醫生的核酸檢測為「陽性、無症狀」。目前這3名醫生正接受集中隔離醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n此外，官方已追蹤到與王女密切接觸者15人，與劉、張、周3名醫生密切接觸者53人，均接受集中隔離醫學觀察中。<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200402/X6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200402%2FX6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=40175928\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200402%2FX6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM%2F&h=08aa5ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200402/X6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM/</a>"},{"pid":"636070c6e15fa072990b91fca958dc61f5f2e9e3","tid":1973430,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzJVibA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzJVibA.jpg&h=af380016&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36811cd4791ca018b043a2745275c83fa9cb51ff","tid":1973430,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"二度封城 可以期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34eb5d37516af857de8e5f57f5cdebd0a7a4b90","tid":1973430,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:54:45.000Z","msg":"快啲復工復課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc392c300267c4931bd40904e3c719b2716a959","tid":1973430,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34eb5d37516af857de8e5f57f5cdebd0a7a4b90","tid":1973430,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:54:45.000Z","msg":"快啲復工復課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da7f245b909e0ee7e428d6a93a21561e5de3355","tid":1973430,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f97a11b49a3b314baeb4deee1bdb9ccc734719","tid":1973430,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face